review_blob: What are you whinging about you beer boring bastards.  Having been in the Royal Australian Navy and having drank every beer in Australia, NZ, and the whole of the Pacific Rim, furthermore being a passionate QLD nder, I can say if your buying a beer to sniff then save your money and get a litre of unleaded petrol, otherwise TED ies are top score for the rest of the criteria, taste, value, and even appearance, you cannot complain.  This is the best Australian (near premium) full strength beer on the market.  Wake up you sad pricks and move on.
